msgstr "Ymse valg"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open folders in separate windows"
msgstr "Åpne mapper i separate vinduer"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:36
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If this option is checked, a new &konqueror; window will be created when "
#| "you open a folder, rather than simply showing that folder's contents in "
#| "the current window."
msgid ""
"If this option is checked, a new &konqueror; window will be created when you "
"open a folder, rather than simply showing that folder’s contents in the "
"current window."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du velger dette, blir det åpnet et nytt &konqueror;-vindu når du åpner "
"en mappe, i stedet for å vise innholdet av mappa i det gamle vinduet."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show “Delete” menu entries which bypass the trashcan"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:43
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Check this if you want <quote>Delete</quote> menu commands to be "
#| "displayed on the desktop and in the file manager's context menus. You can "
#| "always delete files by holding the &Shift; key while calling "
#| "<guimenuitem>Move to Trash</guimenuitem>."
msgid ""
"Check this if you want <quote>Delete</quote> menu commands to be displayed "
"on the desktop and in the file manager’s context menus. You can always "
"delete files by holding the &Shift; key while calling <guimenuitem>Move to "
"Trash</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Her velger du om kommandoen «Slett» skal være med i menyene på skrivebordet "
"og i filbehandlerens kontekstmenyer. Du kan uansett slette filer helt ved å "
"holde nede &Shift;-tasten mens du velger <guimenuitem>Flytt til papirkurven</"
"guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:48
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The settings for &konqueror;'s file manager mode on the <guilabel>View "
#| "Modes</guilabel>, <guilabel>Navigation</guilabel>, <guilabel>Services</"
#| "guilabel>, <guilabel>General</guilabel> and <guilabel>Trash</guilabel> "
#| "pages are used by &dolphin; as well."
msgid ""
"The settings for &konqueror;’s file manager mode on the <guilabel>View "
"Modes</guilabel>, <guilabel>Navigation</guilabel>, <guilabel>Services</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>General</guilabel> and <guilabel>Trash</guilabel> pages "
"are used by &dolphin; as well."
